1.11
log
@retire sparc manuals
@
text
@.\"     $OpenBSD: daadio.4,v 1.10 2014/01/21 03:15:46 schwarze Exp $
.\"
.\" Copyright (c) 2002 Jason L. Wright (jason@@thought.net)
